snippet.title: DogeRift Gameplay Video
snippet.description:
In this video you´re experiencing the gameplay of DogeRift - The cutest NFT Play-To-Earn Game On The Neo Blockchain!
Play a cute Dog(e), have fun with your friends and earn some cryptocurrency at the same time. You can either sell it or use it to power up your Doge.

Each character/skin has different abilities. For example: The mage can see treasure chests.

Want to know more about DogeRift?
Homepage: https://dogerift.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/DogeRift or 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/just1337develop
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/SwztdKh5nC

Beta Start: 6th December 2022
